Can we talk about this hoodie for a sec? 👀 The fit? Next level.

The fabric is premium heavyweight cotton – super soft on the skin but still holds that perfect structure 🤌

And the coolest part?
It has a built-in balaclava hood, which lowkey gives it a whole different vibe🔥

What I really love is that it’s minimal yet bold. No loud graphics, just a clean design with that perfect oversized cut that works with literally everything – cargos, denim, or even layered under a jacket.

Available now on www.kinoh.in

Go grab yours before it sells out.
